title: HDRsoft Photomatix Pro 5.0.5a (x32/x64) [ENG] [Serial]
description:
Standalone program to create HDR photos and adjust them to the look you want, from natural to artistic. Includes advanced editing features and Plugin for Lightroom. 

 - Merge to HDR, Tone Mapping and Exposure Fusion
 - Automatic Alignment of hand-held photos
 - Automatic Ghost Removal and Selective Deghosting tool
 - Automation with Batch Processing
 - Lightroom Plugin
